Package: cockpit-snapraid
Version: VERSION
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: cockpit-bridge (>= 137)
Maintainer: sloraris <sloraris@users.noreply.github.com>
Homepage: https://github.com/sloraris/cockpit-snapraid
Description: SnapRAID status and controls for Cockpit
 Native Cockpit page for snapraid-daemon's local REST API. Shows array and
 disk status, SMART health summaries, sync/scrub/diff controls, task
 history, and daemon configuration, without exposing snapraid-daemon's
 own unauthenticated web UI on the network.
